urdu transliteration text:
KARBALA ZINDA RAHEGI ZINDA RAHENGE MATAMI(KARBALA WILL REMAIN ALIVE, THE ‘MATAMIS’ WILL FOREVER REMAIN ALIVE)English Transliteration
@HujjatELC
Karbala Zinda Rahegi – Karbala will remain alive

Karbala Zinda Rahegi Zinda Rahenge MatamiKARBALA WILL REMAIN ALIVE, THE ‘MATAMIS’ WILL FOREVER REMAIN ALIVE
@HujjatELC
Karbal Ki Kahaani Jab Koi Bhi Sunayega- Whenever the Story of Karbala is Narrated

Karbala Zinda Rahegi Zinda Rahenge MatamiKARBALA WILL REMAIN ALIVE, THE ‘MATAMIS’ WILL FOREVER REMAIN ALIVE
@HujjatELC
Karbal Ki Kahaani Jab Koi Bhi Sunayega- Whenever the Story of Karbala is Narrated

Karbala mojiz numa hai, matami hai mojizaEk azadari ka markaz, ek mujassam hai azaSaaibaan dono pe har dam, Bibi Zahra ki duaJab talak baqi hai dunya, Aur uske baad bhiKARBALA IS A MIRACLE, AND MATAMIS ARE THE MANIFESTATION OF THIS MIRACLEONE IS THE CENTRE FOR AZADARI, ONE IS AZADARI PERSONIFIED THE PRAYERS OF BIBI FATIMA (AS) WILL FOREVER PROTECT THE AZADARSAS LONG AS THIS WORLD REMAINSAND EVEN THEREAFTER
