Karbala me Fatima Zahra ka ghar luta gayaIs liye sab matami karte hai yeh matam bapa Kat gaye ghazi ke bazuKhoon me akbar ke gesuHogaye qasim ke tukdeTHE HOUSE OF FATIMA (AS) WAS DESTROYED IN KARBALAHENCE THE MATAMIS MOURN AND LAMENT IN KARBALATHE ARMS OF ABBAS WERE SEVEREDAKBAR’S HAIR WAS FULL OF BLOODQASIM’S BODY WAS IN PIECES
